@DATABASE "Klax"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - K - Klax"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - K
                   ====================================

                                   Klax
                                   ====



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Credits" rxs "address command zxampoke(59143,0)"}        59143,0
@{"Credits = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(37118,255)"}        37118,x (x= 1- 255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
